{"tid":896812,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下ram既問題 感謝","createTime":"2018-11-10T11:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T14:18:56.000Z","uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd46dd2da89839117e34d88545b4de26b384c6a2","tid":896812,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"我而家用緊<br />\nKingston HyperX Fury 16GB DDR4 2400 Memory Kit (8GB x2)<br />\n<br />\n底板係ASUS Z170 gaming<br />\n睇過最高可支援3400mhz <br />\n<br />\nCpu用緊6700k<br />\n部機就2年前砌 應該玩多1-2年先<br />\n<br />\n咁我平時開chrome好多分頁 同會開住youtube聽歌打機<br />\n有時lag lag地<br />\n而家想加多兩條8gb ram<br />\n<br />\n我就諗住買兩條3000mhz或者以上<br />\n用黎遲upgrade部電腦都可以留返<br />\n<br />\n我爬左文話唔同牌子都ok<br />\nmhz唔同就會拎最底果條既數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家買返兩條一樣既好<br />\n定係有無巴打推介兩條俾我好<br />\nBudget想預1500內 (原來我兩條ram兩年前買$699)<br />\nSorry 好多字 thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16214a5c8567d7b886c81598fc4a489377a74b1","tid":896812,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"newegg"},{"pid":"882993dbe3bf337046ae799df4d87c1b4b5a4518","tid":896812,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"Lag機未必關個ram事 <br />\n你有無試過開 「資源管理器」，mon下你係咁開chrome tab既時候，邊個地方會爆100%式接近100%，果個先係樽頸位。"},{"pid":"424dabfc3ad7a2915f273ce1b108a61f81f10ee7","tid":896812,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"882993dbe3bf337046ae799df4d87c1b4b5a4518","tid":896812,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"Lag機未必關個ram事 <br />\n你有無試過開 「資源管理器」，mon下你係咁開chrome tab既時候，邊個地方會爆100%式接近100%，果個先係樽頸位。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"因為正常16GB ram應該無可能唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid